headline: FAA reopens El Paso airspace, Unity stock plunges on AI fears
summary: Yahoo Finance's John Hyland tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) lifting its airspace closure over El Paso, Texas, and Unity Software (U) shares plunge nearly 30% in Wednesday's session over AI fears cited in its outlook. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
